The wheelchairs will be traveling from Tokyo to Bangkok carrying the hard work of passionate volunteers from high school students to ANA cabin attendants with them. Through the "Flying Wheelchairs" program, the repurposed wheelchairs will be gifted to children and seniors who are not able to afford the device.
